      非推奨です。 
      This method is deprecated and is not used by YARN internally any more. To create a proxy to the RM, use ClientRMProxy#createRMProxy or ServerRMProxy#createRMProxy. Create a proxy to the ResourceManager at the specified address.

    • メソッドの詳細

      • createRMProxy

        @Deprecated
public static <T> T createRMProxy(Configuration conf,
                                              Class<T> protocol,
                                              InetSocketAddress rmAddress)
                                       throws IOException
        非推奨です。 This method is deprecated and is not used by YARN internally any more. To create a proxy to the RM, use ClientRMProxy#createRMProxy or ServerRMProxy#createRMProxy. Create a proxy to the ResourceManager at the specified address.
        型パラメータ:
        T - Type information of the proxy
        パラメータ:
        conf - Configuration to generate retry policy
        protocol - Protocol for the proxy
        rmAddress - Address of the ResourceManager
        戻り値:
        Proxy to the RM
        例外:
        IOException
